g.aria-label: Enter the neighborhood. Between these steps, you will always be at an intersection. Drive three blocks forward, then turn right and drive three more blocks forward. Go the Way of the Cow for a block. Turn left and drive forward. Watch out for that speed hump! Come grinding to a halt right before it. Make a U-turn and drive for a block. Turn right and drive forward a block. Wow, look at that sign on your left!
